item.title: Sorting Algorithms
item.description: Sorting algorithms seem like a great place to get started writing about algorithms. They are easy enough to visualize, explain, and the code is engrained in my mind like the back of my own hand. This note is a work in progress, but will eventually contain all of the sorting algorithms known to man! Well, sort of… Bubble Sort First on the list is fun ol’ bubble sort!

item.title: Computer Science
